lead_paragraph: Canadian Brooke Henderson birdied her first three holes and the final one Thursday for a 6-under 67 and a share of the early first-round lead at the Australian Ladies Masters.

headline.print_headline: Henderson Tied for Early Lead at Australian Ladies Masters
